<heading>inv - Show your inventory.</heading>
<rule/>
<heading level="2">Usage</heading>
<pre>inv</pre>
<heading level="2">Description</heading>
<paragraph>Lists all portable boxes you are currently carrying.</paragraph>
<heading level="2">Examples</heading>
<pre>inv
  Show your inventory.</pre>
<heading level="2">See also</heading>
<paragraph>drop, look, move, place, take</paragraph>
